Package: rfastmongo
Title: Provides utilities for building mongo query using R code
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: person("Tomasz", "Cholewik", email = "tomasz.cholewik@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Allows building queries for MongoDB queries using R functions rather than 
    expect developer to write query as a properly formated string.
Depends: R (>= 3.2.0)
License: GPL-3 + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Suggests: devtools, testthat, covr
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
Imports: jsonlite, purrr, magrittr, assertthat
